{"tid":579893,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"地板濕滑跌一跤　36FF巨乳真的彈出來","createTime":"2018-03-04T04:38:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T09:44:40.000Z","uid":34498,"like":16,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"35c537187a0a92a22ce377d6c986a29d5f4cbfab","tid":579893,"uid":34498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T04:38:38.000Z","msg":"英國真人秀女星西娜(Bex Shiner)又有驚人動作，這次她不慎走在濕滑地板，更因此跌一跤，還讓36FF巨乳走光，真的「彈粗奶」。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《鏡報》報導，當時西娜正準備赴約，並從飯店房間走出，但沒注意到濕滑地板，也沒在意警示黃牌，隨後西娜就不小心摔了一跤。這時，36FF奶很自動地彈出來，底褲也被狗仔記者拍到，西娜向狗仔們請求手下留情，之後還把警示黃牌放在走道中央，希望別人注意，不要和她一樣打滑摔跤。<br />\n<br />\n西娜曾是護士，之後參加真人秀節目走紅，現在轉戰AV女優事業。不過西娜的行徑一向以誇張著稱，她先前曾當街自行扒衣，裸露上半身，彈出36FF巨乳，更坐在地上飲酒，動作相當不雅觀。西娜還曾經因為遇到一名瘋狂粉絲，對她潑灑麵粉，而西娜的衣服也就順勢滑下來，讓她當場露出胸前巨乳<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180301/640_e3a196f8fcfa0ea4dedf1d3068bf3a1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180301%2F640_e3a196f8fcfa0ea4dedf1d3068bf3a1a.jpg&h=b14c011c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f32a47d7192df70d118bd82724546e272120f086","tid":579893,"uid":13689,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T04:42:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cbu01.alicdn.com/img/ibank/2017/449/910/3922019944_1851547910.220x220.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcbu01.alicdn.com%2Fimg%2Fibank%2F2017%2F449%2F910%2F3922019944_1851547910.220x220.jpg&h=91ee1747&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a4e53409617d84f5dc98d42d2243f8e686dcd0fc","tid":579893,"uid":140411,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T04:43:44.000Z","msg":"從來沒我份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57169444690fb9793c6225a1e2176628cf523d52","tid":579893,"uid":55533,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T04:45:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/f/fe/203237_ca97e44be069f5d9cf6ba9b272cd4d82.jpg/revision/latest?